<div id='admin_sub_wrap'>
	<h2>메타태그 도움말</h2>

	<div id='reserve_search_wrap' style='padding:25px;'>
		<div class='source_area'>
			<p style="font-size: 15px !important;"><strong>메타태그의 종류</strong></p>
			<p>1. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"generator"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"페이지 제작툴"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>2. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"author"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"제작자"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>3. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"keywords"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"메타키워드"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p style="color:#888">   &nbsp;&nbsp; -> 1개 이상의 키워드를 넣을 때는 ,(콤마) 등을 사용하면 된다.</p>
			<p style="color:#888">   &nbsp;&nbsp; -> 예) 창업,마케팅,소셜미디어,...</p>
			<p>4.<span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"description"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"페이지 요약설명"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>			
			<p style="color:#888">   &nbsp;&nbsp; -> 반드시 메타키워드에서 사용한 키워드들로 작성하여야 한다.</p>
			<p>5. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"copyright"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"저작권 정보"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>6. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"subject"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"웹사이트 주제 입력"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>7. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"title"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"웹사이트 이름"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>8. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"publicher"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"만든단체 또는 회사"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>9. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"other agent"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"웹사이트 책임자"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>10. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"classification"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"카테고리 분류"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>11. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"reply-to(email)"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"메일주소"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>12. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"filename"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"파일이름 입력"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>13. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"author-date(date)"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"제작일"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>14. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"location"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"위치/대한민국인지등 나라이름기록"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>
			<p>15. <span class="blue">&lt;meta</span> <span class="red">name=</span><span class="magenta">"distribution"</span> <span class="red">content=<span><span class="magenta">"배포자"</span> <span class="blue"> /><span></p>			
			<p style="margin-top: 30px;font-size: 15px !important;"><strong>메타태그 삽입 방법</strong></p>
			<p><span class="blue">&lt;head> &lt;/head></span> 사이에 메타 태그를 작성해서 넣는다.</p>
		</div>
	</div>

